Subject: Re: dual solex

I just installed type 4 empi dual solex carbs on my bus and im getting a pop
corn sound when idling.

Sounds like an air leak causing that side to run lean. Try spraying your
flammable substance of choice (such as WD40) at the joins. The engine revs
will increase when you hit the leak.
